'''Rajesh Gopie,''' ni  umukinnnyi wa firime muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]  uturuka muri  [[Ubuhinde|Indian]] . <ref>https://www.apm.co.za/artiste/rajesh-gopie-1142/</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri serivise za tereviziyo ''Stellenbosch'', ''Professionals'' and ''The World Unseen''

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Durban, muri Afurika y'Epfo mu muryango w'Abahinde. Yabonye impamyabumenyi ya BA mu Cyongereza, Ikinamico n'Amateka muri kaminuza ya Natal . <ref name="esat">https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Rajesh_Gopie</ref>

Muri Nyakanga 2020, nyirasenge Dolly Singh yapfuye afite imyaka 76 azize indwara ya COVID-19. <ref>https://www.pressreader.com/south-africa/post-south-africa/20200708/281479278703101</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Amaze kurangiza amashuri, yimukiye mu [[Bwongereza]] umwaka umwe yiga ikinamico. Amaze gusubira muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo, yakoze ikinamico ''hanze ya Bound'' ivuga ku buzima n'ibihe by'imiryango y'Abahinde bo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. <ref>https://www.loot.co.za/product/rajesh-gopie-out-of-bounds/rjmh-1440-g270</ref>

Amaze gusubira muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], yinjiye mu makinamico menshi nka''Be Proud, Be Yourself'', ''Out of Bounds'' (1999), ''The Coolie Odyssey'' (2002), ''The Tale of the Allergist’s Wife'', ''The Chimp Project'', ''Romeo and Juliet'', ''Back to the Faith'', ''Mahatma vs Gandhi'', ''The Pinter Sketches'', ''The Wiz'' and ''Hamlet'' (2005). Hagati aho, yakoraga nk'umwanditsi w'amakinamico ku makinamico,''Out of Bounds'' (1999), ''Be Proud'', ''Be Yourself Out of Bounds'' (2001), ''Mahatma-Madiba'', ''Marital Bliss'' and ''Too Close for Comfort'' .  Mu 2001, yatsindiye igihembo cyimyandikire myiza y’abasangwabutaka muri Fleur du Cap Theatre Awards kubera ikinamico ''Out of Bound'' . Yayoboye kandi, yandika kandi akina ikinamico izwi cyane ya ''Coolie Odyssey'' mu 2002. <ref>http://www.jayabhattacharjirose.com/tag/rajesh-gopie/</ref>

Muri 2013 yahawe buruse ya Oppenheimer aho yagiye i Londres gukurikirana amasomo ya nyuma. Nyuma yarangije icyiciro cya gatatu  cya kaminuza mu mahugurwa y'abakinnyi no gutoza mu ishuri rikuru rya Royal Central Speech and Drama muri 2014. Muri 2015, yabaye umuyobozi w'ikinamico hamwe na ''Yerma'' ikinamico yanditswe na Federico García Lorca. <ref>https://artlink.co.za/news_article.htm?contentID=37640</ref>

Muri 2017, yakinnye muri firime yo gusetsa yo muri Afurika yepfo ''Gukomeza hamwe na Kandasamys'' iyobowe na Jayan Moodley. Iyi filime ibaye filime ya mbere yo muri Afurika yepfo yerekanwe cyane mu makinamico. Irimo Jailoshini Naidoo, Maeshni Naicker, Madhushan Singh, na Mishqah Parthiephal . Iyi filime yaje kuba filime yinjije amafaranga menshi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] muri 2017, ndetse na filime yo muri Afurika y'Epfo yinjije amafaranga menshi ku isi muri 2017. <ref>https://www.ecr.co.za/news/entertainment/keeping-kandasamys-makes-r16-million-box-office/</ref>

Muri 2018, yagaragaye muri firime yo muri Afurika yepfo yibyaha byibasiye ''Mayfair'' . Yakinnye cyane muri 'Aziz' muri film, nyuma yaje kwakirwa neza. <ref>https://filmfestival.capetown/mayfair/</ref> <ref>https://m.channel24.co.za/Movies/Reviews/mayfair-20181014</ref> Iyi filime kandi yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya 62 rya BFI London na Afurika mu iserukiramuco rya Filime mu Kwakira 2018. <ref>https://www.indianspice.co.za/2018/09/johannesburgs-mayfair-suburb-goes-international-in-new-movie/</ref> <ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2018/11/06/film/business/mayfair-opens-to-great-reviews/</ref>

